{"tid":1417344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勿忘初衷 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:54.000Z","uid":211565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"deee9b2cf4c75293a65f600bd59964d2fc080709","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"好多人問<br />\n依家咁多人支持點解要改口號？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你啦，班啊叔公務員銀髮支持你既初衷唔係光復啊！係五大訴求！</span><br />\n<br />\n你覺得你繼續叫落去佢地會繼續支持？<br />\n777一嘢話你地港獨 佢地就縮架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且好多中立派同有班無上連登既人<br />\n真係未必會明句口號<br />\n佢地第一個反應多數<span style=\"color: navy;\">係聯想起港獨</span><br />\n而好多人正正係好反感港獨<br />\n<br />\n甚至乎外國對於港獨都好敏感<br />\n你講五大訴求都有好多人支持<br />\n但當你一比人屈港獨好多外國就鳩縮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好執著於一句口號</span>，令自己慢慢地失去其他支持者，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1411526345473f8a5ffc4d20743cd76ad7f6b0f1","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. 完全撤回《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n2. 撤回 6.12 暴動定性<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，不可秋後算帳<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，調查警察濫暴濫權、追究警察開槍責任及元朗警黑勾結<br />\n5. 全面落實雙普選。"},{"pid":"4ba0a0109c606a8d585e9b8d016d10e5a1ee82d4","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">完全撤回《逃犯條例》修訂</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4f2654b29411125628a3874b157bdd7dcca2d8e","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"五大訴求先係原來重點，點解要轉風向去革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9d30e0a11f628ad285d2b94316b1486fd03e40","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">追究警黑勾結都係五大訴求之一!</span></span>"},{"pid":"d973ef33b092263d811d9664940645eea6e5c2c8","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">成立獨立委員會徹查警暴</span></span>"},{"pid":"42c4019c767a5fd73cc457f5f92c4a9725cf5e36","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d973ef33b092263d811d9664940645eea6e5c2c8","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">成立獨立委員會徹查警暴</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"即使係藍絲都好支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8459e0856300066827c20bd50fde0ac8b0cc3411","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c4019c767a5fd73cc457f5f92c4a9725cf5e36","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d973ef33b092263d811d9664940645eea6e5c2c8","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">成立獨立委員會徹查警暴</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"即使係藍絲都好支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"幫佢哋還所謂<strong>白警</strong>既清白好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d96f34fe1427faa6d9a835c11cbb05493483c7","tid":1417344,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"大家小心比仇恨沖昏頭腦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dddd082e428ec05d90fa7a1f3515709b9a84c2e","tid":1417344,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RC17pFV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRC17pFV.png&h=a8546f33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2gLbkV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2gLbkV.png&h=a2cfca7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003351_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003351_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=17b2be54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003352_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003352_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=af4400e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/003353_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F003353_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png&h=144d8ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}